== Ingredients
- 9 inch piecrust
- 125 mL milk
- 1 diced medium onion
- 2 cloves minced garlic
- 2 beets
- 3 eggs
- salt
- dill

== Directions
- Boil beets until fork-tender
- Sautee garlic and onions until carmelized
- Puree beets, garlic, and onions
- Mix in eggs and milk while pureeing
- Combine with dill and pour into pie crust
- Bake at $350^circle F$ for 45$+epsilon$ minutes.

